     H            Y.
     F** UTLR32D **********************************************************
     F*  CONVERT CHAR -> REPLACE FIRST ZEROS TO BLANKS                    *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR32D'
     F*                    PARM           PIN    30
     F*                    PARM           POUT   30
     F*   IN  PIN   : 30A    TEXT
     F*   OUT POUT  : 30A    TEXT
     F*   EX.                                                             *
     F*   00000300 --> "_____300    "    REPLACE FIRST ZEROS TO BLANKS    *
     F*********************************************************************
     E                    OUT        30  1
     F******************************************************************
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PIN    30
     C                     PARM           POUT   30
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    POUT
     C                     MOVEAPIN       OUT
     C* SEARCH FIRST
     C           1         DO   30        IX      20
     C           OUT,IX    IFNE '0'
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE ' '       OUT,IX
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVEAOUT       POUT
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
